"Paroubek" budget removed money from income and sickness subsidies
After the left, despite the government’s view, added funds for farmers or officials, there may not be enough money in the budget for income, sickness subsidies or construction savings.
But also not for the interests of state debt or international litigation.
This will hurt everyone who governs in the second half of next year, says Finance Minister Eduard Janota.
