Last year of ČEZ allocated 18,000 million to the budget.
Each year of the dividends ecological damages are settled, serve to complete the account for the rents or serve as a reserve for the prepared income reform.
In addition, with this trick, according to EU rules, the real budget deficit increases to the level of 5.7% of GDP.
