The national headquarters is in Alcobendas (Madrid).
There, more than one hundred technicians (usually mechanical experts) work simultaneously with three computer screens.
Audatex invests 90 million euros per year in the preparation of these databases.
Every month 2.5 million data is included, and customers receive updates every other day.
